      "post_content": "Probably THE most famous card to go into a 'Discard' Deck, ever. Fairly cheap to play, quite effective (2 damage per card adds up very quickly!) and, being a Black Enchantment, it gets a lot of support from a lot of other Black cards.  \n  \nWorks quite well in a multicolor deck too - Black/Blue being the best. Add Megrim to Lore Broker or to Magus of the Vase, and watch the Life points tick away...",
