      "post_content": "This card got completely outclassed by [Liliana's Caress](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Liliana's Caress). Sure, [Megrim](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Megrim) isn't strictly worse in that it is useful in the [Pain Magnification](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pain Magnification)/[Furnace of Rath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Furnace of Rath) combo, but the caress is usually better.",
      "posted_by": "marmaris74",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost237812\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">This card got completely outclassed by <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Liliana's Caress\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Liliana's Caress\">Liliana's Caress</a>. Sure, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Megrim\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Megrim\">Megrim</a> isn't strictly worse in that it is useful in the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pain Magnification\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pain Magnification\">Pain Magnification</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Furnace of Rath\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Furnace of Rath\">Furnace of Rath</a> combo, but the caress is usually better.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '237812'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy64897\">marmaris74</span>\r\n                                (4/15/2012 1:18:09 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRe